IT MAY BE REQUIRED TO MAKE AS PART OF FULFILLING ITS GUARANTEE OBLIGATIONS.

PORTIONS OF CERTAIN LIABILITIES WERE ESTABLISHED IN PRIOR PERIODS AS PART OF THE

COMPANYS SPECIAL CHARGES DUE TO THE EVENTS OF SEPTEMBER 11, 2001.

