EXCESS DEFERRED PRODUCTION COSTS OR UNAMORTIZED TOOLING COSTS NOT RECOVERABLE

FROM EXISTING FIRM ORDERS FOR THE 737 NEXT-GENERATION AND 777 PROGRAMS.

