2001, FUTURE LEASE COMMITMENTS ON AIRCRAFT NOT RECORDED ON THE CONDENSED

CONSOLIDATED STATEMENTS OF FINANCIAL POSITION TOTALED $246 AND $323. THESE LEASE

COMMITMENTS EXTEND THROUGH 2015, AND THE COMPANYS INTENT IS TO RECOVER

THESE LEASE COMMITMENTS THROUGH SUBLEASE ARRANGEMENTS. AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2002

AND 2001, ACCOUNTS PAYABLE AND OTHER LIABILITIES INCLUDED $130 ($2 RELATED TO

THE EVENTS OF SEPTEMBER 11, 2001) AND $116 ($1 RELATED TO THE EVENTS OF

SEPTEMBER 11, 2001) ATTRIBUTABLE TO ADVERSE COMMITMENTS UNDER THESE LEASE

ARRANGEMENTS.

