CERTIFICATES SECURED BY AIRCRAFT ON LEASE TO UNITED AIRLINES, $66 RELATED TO THE

IMPAIRMENT OF 717S RETURNED TO THE COMPANY BY AMR, AND $80 RELATED TO AN

